### Hermes demo requests (VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP client)

### Landscape statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/landscape/statistics

### Landscape warnings — the intentional cycle and single-source consumers
GET http://localhost:8080/landscape/warnings

### Full health map
GET http://localhost:8080/landscape/health-map

### THE demo: SAP ECC goes down completely
POST http://localhost:8080/analysis/impact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "system": "SAP_ECC",
  "degradationType": "COMPLETE_OUTAGE"
}

### Retrieve a stored report (replace the id)
GET http://localhost:8080/analysis/impact/{{reportId}}

### Recovery sequence for a system sitting on the cycle
POST http://localhost:8080/analysis/recovery-sequence
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "system": "LEGACY_WMS"
}

### Register a new system at runtime
POST http://localhost:8080/landscape/systems
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "PRICING_SERVICE",
  "name": "Dynamic Pricing Service",
  "type": "API",
  "businessCriticality": 6,
  "description": "Microservice for promotional pricing"
}

### Wire it into the landscape
POST http://localhost:8080/landscape/integrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "IFL-100",
  "name": "Price Push to CRM",
  "source": "PRICING_SERVICE",
  "target": "SALESFORCE",
  "protocol": "REST",
  "dataType": "PriceBook",
  "businessProcess": "Order to Cash",
  "criticality": 5,
  "slaClass": "NEAR_REAL_TIME"
}

### Reset all statuses to HEALTHY
POST http://localhost:8080/landscape/reset
